Hello Eddie    The inner part is made curved and the outter skin is flat and 
is easy to bend into place.  I would suggest that you cut out the front skin 
below the lip and check the inner section as it usually rusts out.  Try kelly 
Brown  Metal wizard  . I have done a bunch of these. later and have fun  mark 
